ED_Title: Maintenance of international security – good neighbourliness, stability and development in South-Eastern Europe
ED_DecisionText:
At its 51st plenary meeting, on 5 December 2016, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the First Committee,  decided to include in the provisional agenda of its seventy-third session the item entitled “Maintenance of international security – good-neighbourliness, stability and development in South-Eastern Europe”.

(See A/71/444, para 7; A/71/PV.51)
ED_Disclaimer: The text of this decision is available in all languages in document A/71/49 (Vol. II).
